data.description: 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a HUGE fenced-in back yard and shop! This home boasts a smooth floor plan with easy flow, split bedrooms, and new updates. The new flooring gives this home a nice modern and clean feel, while the spacious kitchen with tons of cabinets and counter space gives tons of storage and a perfect gathering place in the heart of the home. The appliances will convey with this one, even the Refrigerator and the WASHER AND DRYER! Be sure to check the photos of the large backyard, Fire pit, and shop that is great for storage, carport, or perfect spot to set up for fall get-togethers. All you need to bring is the marshmallows. Pack your bags move right into this move-in ready home, and just relax.
